item.description:
@Assassins_Creed_Fan wrote:

[quote=“the elve age, post:20, topic:268285”]OFF TOPIC: A.C.F & krackkid, why in the world would you just want an argument over a GAME’S FORUMS?
I mean no point to bring someone down…Im sure when you guys started modeling you guys began at recoloring and adding stuff together?

ON TOPIC: Even if krack and A.C.F are right…you sure did a hell of a job recoloring and adding things together lol[/quote]We aren’t(well i am not) trying to put down people.
We are trying to learn them not to recolour/reshape models , because you will get allot of unwanted message’s on your Thread/Topic.

Sure i did recolour items, but it was a big mistake in my begin of modelling.
People discouraged me because they tought i was a leecher/recolourer.
I just don’t want people to get discouraged because they make the big mistake to recolour/reshape.

I want to get people good at modelling by posting such message’s as don’t recolour.
Because if they do recolour…
It will give you allot of mean posts .
People won’t respect you and will want you to leave the forums ASAP.
I’m not putting him down.
I’m trying to learn him basic knowledge
